Package: ambolt
Title: Web Applications with R and Svelte
Version: 0.1.0.9036
Authors@R: person("Love", "Hansson", email = "love.hansson@transportforetagen.se",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Build reactive web applications using R for the backend and
    Svelte 5 for the frontend. Provides a declarative DSL for layouts,
    inputs, outputs, and themes. The framework generates Svelte components
    from R declarations and serves them via ambiorix.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
